    "user_title": "Write detailed PR descriptions with visual elements",
    "value_statement": "Writing clear, comprehensive PR descriptions takes significant time and effort. This skill automates the creation of reviewer-friendly descriptions using structured formatting, visual diagrams, and organized sections.",
